IN RE RAYMOND L. FRICK TRUST. Edward M. Kress and Jenny Frick Trychel, a/k/a Jeni Frick Trychel, Successor Co-Trustees, Plaintiffs-Appellees,
v.
Bradley Spice and BCL 75, Inc., Defendants-Appellants. SC: 158984
COA: 341498 Supreme Court of Michigan. September 10, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the motion for reconsideration of this Court's May 28, 2019 order is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that reconsideration of our previous order is warranted. MCR 7.311(G).
